{"tid":622591,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[放負] 俾個識咗好多年嘅兄弟出賣","createTime":"2018-04-09T09:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T15:54:40.000Z","uid":97606,"like":7,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e227b30c4dfa941de26e270bc9a9541269e5087c","tid":622591,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:05:04.000Z","msg":"細佬今年考DSE，<br />\n雖然自覺準備唔係好夠，<br />\n但係我自問有盡好每分每秒做好自己，對得住自己良心，<br />\n之前我中學一路都有個兄弟，<br />\n每日放學打波打機吹水飲可樂，一齊答應話會讀同一間大學，<br />\n仲要study leave日日出嚟溫書，以為關係會好好唔<br />\n點知我早幾日考試嗰陣影咗張snapchat俾佢，<br />\n佢睇完之後即時cap咗我圖，之後block晒我聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n我之後用朋友FB問佢做咩，<br />\n佢問翻我轉頭話: 你唔知你自己影到張barcode咩?<br />\n我答佢話無留意到，亦唔係特登影。<br />\n我跟住問佢想點，佢話會直接去擺上網同report我。<br />\n我問佢點解要咁做，佢答我一句試場如戰場，無人會一世都做到好朋友，仲話我自己衰on9自求多福，唔可以怪佢。<br />\n<br />\n咁我可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e840f0f033d6145214cebdbc991ea68aa8a8b8","tid":622591,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"諗咁多做乜打個靚J就乜事都無架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c820b3135f37d6d77a9c6580761abcddf0f031","tid":622591,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:06:50.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c72cda568e62fea6909fa62b7dd59b79072696","tid":622591,"uid":5623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的 0分重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0c160224020f09e24fabf272f30715af85bb4a","tid":622591,"uid":119605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bce3296fb17e67a9d21b64f2a69468c5401251","tid":6225